title: 756. Most Dangerous Wild Card Teams & Reaction to Monday Games
itunes:title: 756. Most Dangerous Wild Card Teams & Reaction to Monday Games
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode of Move the Sticks. To start off, the guys discuss load management due to a longer season and all the COVID-19 cases. Next, the duo react to the two Monday games of the Las Vegas Raiders vs. Cleveland Browns and the Minnesota Vikings vs. Chicago Bears. After that, the pair explain how the Indianapolis Colts roster is built different. To wrap up the show, the guys emphasize which wild card teams are the most dangerous.


Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.
